specials.description:
Saving Throw Fortitude DC 15; 
Exposing the victim to sunlight or any light spell of 3rd level or higher pauses the progress of the disease until the victim is no longer in light. 
Stage 1 carrier with no effect (1d6 hours); 
Stage 2 victim’s hair falls out (1d6 hours); 
Stage 3 ears grow into leathery wings, tentacles sprout on the chin and scalp, and the teeth become long, pointed fangs (1 day); 
Stage 4 victim’s mind regresses to a vicious and unintelligent shell of its former self (1d6 hours);
Stage 5 victim’s head breaks free of the body (which dies) and becomes a new %.
